GET http://localhost:3000/api/node/current

### Git 状态
GET http://localhost:3000/api/git/status

### Git 配置
GET http://localhost:3000/api/git/config

### 项目列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects

### 系统目录选择器信息
GET http://localhost:3000/api/system/directory-picker

### Swagger 文档
GET http://localhost:3000/api-docs
